dockerz (2.75.0-1) jammy; urgency=medium

  * Major release with comprehensive Git operations enhancement and testing completion.
  * Added advanced Git change detection for complex scenarios: tag-based changes, branch-specific detection, cherry-pick handling, and git reset recovery.
  * Enhanced logging system providing excellent transparency into all Git operations and build processes.
  * Completed comprehensive QA testing across all 50 scenarios with 100% success rate.
  * Improved Git tracking depth configuration and cross-branch operation handling.
  * Enhanced smart build orchestration with better service isolation and change detection precision.
  * Added robust handling of complex Git repository states and edge cases.
  * Improved build optimization with better cache utilization and performance scaling.
  * Enhanced error handling and stability across all advanced Git scenarios.
  * Added support for enhanced logging and debugging capabilities.

 -- Adhbhut Gupta <adhbutg@gmail.com>  Sat, 23 Nov 2025 21:23:00 +0530

dockerz (2.0.0-1) jammy; urgency=medium

  * Major version bump to 2.0 with complete rewrite in Go.
  * Added smart build features: git change detection, multi-level caching, and smart orchestration.
  * Added automatic image name normalization to Docker-compatible kebab-case.
  * Added CI/CD integration with --changed-services-file and --output-changed-services flags.
  * Added new CLI flags: --smart, --git-track, --cache, --force, --project-id, --region, --gar-name, --tag, --changed-services-file, --output-changed-services.
  * Enhanced configuration with smart features support.
  * Improved build performance with intelligent service filtering.
  * Migrated from Python to Go for better performance and maintainability.

 -- Adhbhut Gupta <adhbutg@gmail.com>  Sun, 27 Oct 2025 12:00:00 +0530

